SyncPriceFromOracle_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── given null
│  └── it should revert
└── given not null
   ├── given SETTLED
   │  └── it should revert
   ├── given EXPIRED
   │  └── it should revert
   └── given ACTIVE
      ├── when latest price zero
      │  └── it should do nothing
      └── when latest price not zero
         ├── it should return the latest price
         ├── it should update the last synced price
         ├── it should update the last synced timestamp
         └── it should emit a {SyncPriceFromOracle} event
